---
import DiscordCard from "../ui/DiscordCard.astro";
---
<section id="tab-live" class="tab-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:6px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
      FWC
      <span class="live-badge-header">EN VIVO</span>
    </h2>
  </div>

  <div class="live-quality-notice">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
    <span>¿Quieres una transmisión más estable y en <strong>Full HD 1080P</strong>? Únete a nuestro servidor de Discord <strong>WCC UES · Copa del Mundo 2026</strong>.</span>
  </div>

  <div class="live-body">
    <div class="live-player-wrap" id="live-player-wrap"></div>

    <div class="live-discord-section">
      <DiscordCard description="Transmisión en Full HD 1080P y sigue los partidos con la comunidad 🏆" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
